criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  with diagnosis of HF or hospitalized for acute HF

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  degenerative neurological diseases;

          -  patients with renal / hepatic / pulmonary or systemic disease that may confuse the
             interpretation of findings or result in limited life expectancy;

          -  surgical or therapeutic plan that may influence the follow-up;

          -  pregnancy;

          -  diagnosis of acute HF secondary to: sepsis, myocarditis, acute myocardial infarction,
             peripartum and other acute cause;

          -  not be able to contact by phone.
